Package edu.metrostate.ics372.thatgroup.clinicaltrial.views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPatientView
    This view is responsible for displaying the form to add a new patient to the system
    ClinicalTrialView
    This View is the main wrapper for the user interface and is responsible for holding the the various views
    ClinicalTrialViewModel
    The ClinicalTrialViewModel is a class that provides a central means of access to all of the information that a clinical trial provides.
    PatientsView
    This view is responsible for displaying the patients in a ListView for the user to select to view or add readings
    PopupNotification
    A utility class to pop-up a message on the screen.
    ReadingsView
    This view is responsible for displaying the readings in a TableView for a selected patient
    ReadingView
    This view is responsible for taking user input for a new patient reading.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StringResource
    Holds string literals used in the implementation of the user interface
